import "./EditAgent.css"; import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import { faTrash, faPencilAlt } from "@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons"; import { Form, Row, Col, Button, InputGroup, Image } from "react-bootstrap"; import { FontAwesomeIcon } from "@fortawesome/react-fontawesome"; import { useDispatch, useSelector } from "react-redux"; import { useParams } from "react-router-dom"; import { getAgentByEmail } from "../../reducers/AgentReducer"; function EditAgent() { let { email } = useParams(); const dispatch = useDispatch(); useEffect(() => { dispatch(getAgentByEmail(email)); }, [email]); const { agentById } = useSelector((state) => state.agent); return (
Email Name DOB CRM Id Telecalling ID Address License URN no. License Issue Date License Expiry Date
); } export default EditAgent;
